languages.text: {n}Юноша вздыхает.{/n} "Останки моего отряда. Когда мы покончим с мятежом, им окажут почести как павшим в праведном бою".
{n}The young man sighs.{/n} "The remains of my squad. Once we've put down the rebellion, they'll be given the last honours they deserve as soldiers fallen in a righteous battle."

languages.text: {n}Der junge Mann seufzt.{/n} "Die Überreste meines Trupps. Wenn wir die Rebellion niedergeschlagen haben, bekommen sie die letzte Ehre, die sie verdient haben. Sie sind in einer rechtschaffenen Schlacht als Soldaten gefallen."
languages.original_text: {n}The young man sighs.{/n} "The remains of my squad. Once we've put down the rebellion, they'll be given the last honours they deserve as soldiers fallen in a righteous battle."

languages.text: {n}Le jeune homme soupire.{/n} « C'est tout ce qu'il reste de mon escouade. Quand nous aurons écrasé la révolte, ils recevront les derniers honneurs que méritent des soldats tombés au champ d'honneur. »

languages.text: {n}年轻人叹了口气。{/n}“那些都是我战友的尸体，他们在正义的战争中牺牲了。等我们解决这场叛乱之后，所有人都会得到应有的荣耀。”
languages.original_text: {n}The young man sighs.{/n} "The remains of my squad. Once we've put down the rebellion, they'll be given the last honours they deserve as soldiers fallen in a righteous battle."

languages.text: {n}若者は、ため息をつく。{/n}「私の部隊だ…反乱を鎮圧したら、彼らは正義の戦いで散った兵士にふさわしい最後の栄誉を与えられるだろう」

languages.text: {n}El joven suspira.{/n} «Los restos de mi escuadrón. Una vez que hayamos acabado con la rebelión, se les rendirán los últimos honores que merecen como soldados caídos en una batalla justa».

languages.text: {n}Genç adam iç çekiyor.{/n} "Mangamdakilerin naaşları. İsyanı bastırdığımızda, erdemli bir savaşta şehit düşen askerler olarak kahramanlıklarına layık bir cenaze töreniyle şereflendirilecekler."
